fragment ProductsEditProduct on ProductNode {
  id
  name
  description
  category
  price
  count
  isAddNutritionalValue

  carbs

  weight

query ProductsEditGetProduct($id: String!) {
  object: product(id: $id) {

    __typename
  }
}
